casebody.data:
Johnny E. SETZER
v.
STATE of North Carolina and John McDivett, Sheriff of Burke County, and Gary Dellinger, District Attorney for Burke and Office of Attorney General for North Carolina. No. 115P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 16, 2006. Johnny Setzer, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of NC. Gary Dellinger, District Attorney, Pro Se. John McDivett, Sheriff of Burke County, Pro Se.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Plaintiff on the 10th day of March 2006 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Burke County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 16th day of March 2006."
